they we're guarded by dogs at

Broadway. was shot through the

side an east side market and
was in serious condition at Mar.
icopa Hospital.


Her cousin, Augusta Emmit
Bryant, 46. Of 2542 E. Pueblo.
was jailed for investigation Of
assault with a deadly weapon.
police said.


Witnesses told police the
shooting followed an argument
between Bryant and Miss Will
liams while they sat in a car In
front of the AIM Market al
1905 E. Wood.


Bryant asked store clerk to
call police after the shooting
occurred. Police said Bryant told
them he shot his cousin with .
32-caliber pistol after she
threatened him with a razor.
